We will need:

1) VPC
2) EKS Control Plane
3) Worker capacity management
4) Terraform state file in S3


Tools: 
AWS Services: IAM, VPC, EKS, EC2, ENI, S3, KMS keys
Installations: Terraform, AWS Cli, kubectl, eksctl


Terraform directory layout: 
    --Environment
      --Non_Prod
        -main.tf
        -variables.tf
        -terraform.tfvars
        -backend.tf




